            "body": "Couple of notes:\n- You need to toggle the preview to trigger this bug or add `--preview-window=nohidden` to the job start args.\n- This messes up my neovim so good even after leaving the term the window is covered with overflow blocks, the only way to solve this is to restart neovim (:redraw doesn’t help):\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/42913f3f-39f7-4202-9f52-77ccb2aec3d7)\n\nAfter exiting the term:\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/76d2ad34-c9b6-455f-95d0-e30fbe36694a)",
